data.description: Welcome home to this 4 bed, 3 bath spacious split-level home in the highly sought after Sterling Ponds neighborhood! Offering space for the whole family with over 2700 sq. ft. Light and bright with neutral colors in this wonderful home, which features vaulted ceilings, cozy gas fireplace, main floor laundry & more! Main floor master suite with new/updated master bath (2024) and walk-in closet. Floors updated on the main floor, with open kitchen/dining area leading out to the deck. Black stainless appliances, granite counters, gas stovetop. Walkout lower level has 2 huge bedrooms and a large family room with walk-up bar to entertain. Completely fenced in yard for privacy/pets. Heated/insulated garage. Great location, only 1 block from park. New roof 2022. Quick close possible.
